## AKC Real Estate — Project Summary

**What it is:** A single-page marketing/landing website for **AKC Real Estate**, a Chennai-based firm selling **CMDA-approved residential plots**. Built with Next.js 16 (App Router), React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4, GSAP, and Framer Motion.

### Page Structure (9 sections in `page.tsx`)

1. **Navbar** — Fixed, transparent-to-white on scroll, mobile hamburger menu (Framer Motion)
2. **HeroSection** — Full-viewport hero with Unsplash bg, GSAP entrance animation, "Contact Now" CTA
3. **ValuePropsSection** — 4 feature cards: CMDA Approved, Best Rates, Secure & Legal, Prime Locations
4. **GallerySection** — 12-image masonry grid, click-to-open Lightbox with keyboard nav
5. **CTABanner** — Green gradient with WhatsApp CTA (`wa.me/+919876543210` placeholder)
6. **ReviewsSection** — 8 hardcoded 5-star reviews, CSS `@keyframes` infinite horizontal scroll
7. **AboutAKC** — Company story with animated counter stats (IntersectionObserver)
8. **ContactSection** — Contact info + Google Maps embed + form (client-side only, no backend)
9. **Footer** — Dark green footer with brand, links, services, social icons (all `#` placeholders)

### Key Observations

- **No backend at all** — contact form is cosmetic (clears on submit, shows toast, no API call)
- **All placeholder data** — phone, email, WhatsApp, social links are fake/defaults
- **Stock images only** — all gallery/hero images are Unsplash URLs
- **No dynamic routes** — single page only, no sub-pages for projects or individual plots
- **GSAP + Framer Motion coexist** — GSAP for timelines/scroll-triggers, Framer Motion for scroll reveals and mobile menu
- **Decent accessibility** — `prefers-reduced-motion` respected, semantic sections, `aria-label`s, proper form labels
- **Tailwind v4** — CSS-first config via `@theme inline`, no `tailwind.config.ts`
